 reading it as a degrading chapter in Latin American Jewish history, Impure Migration interrogates a complicated social landscape to reveal that sex work is in fact a critical part of the histories of migration, labor, race, and sexuality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aHuman traffickingxHistory. 0aJewish womenzArgentina. 0aJewsxMigrationsxHistory. 0aJewszArgentinazBuenos AiresxHistoryy19th century. 0aJewszArgentinazBuenos AiresxHistoryy20th century. 0aJews, EuropeanzArgentinazBuenos AiresxHistory. 0aProstitutionzArgentinazBuenos AiresxHistory. 0aSocial reformerszArgentinazBuenos AiresxHistory. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2019 Englishz978311061017808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2019z9783110606195oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertRutgers University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065352640uhttps://doi.org/10.36019/9780813598185zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780813598185423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780813598185.jpg  a978-3-11-061017-8  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-065352-6  Rutgers University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019